Stone Gossard - Rhythm Guitar (1990&lt;U+2013&gt;Present)
Mike McCready - Lead Guitar (1990&lt;U+2013&gt;Present)
Eddie Vedder - Lead Vocals, Guitar, Harmonica (1990&lt;U+2013&gt;Present)
Matt Cameron - Drums (1998&lt;U+2013&gt;Present)

Other members

Boom Gaspar - Hammond B3 and Keyboards (2002&lt;U+2013&gt;Present)

Former members

Dave Krusen - Drums (1990&lt;U+2013&gt;1991)
Matt Chamberlain - Drums (1991)
Dave Abbruzzese - Drums (1991&lt;U+2013&gt;1994)
