1993: Video of the Year - &quot;Jeremy&quot;
1993: Best Group Video - &quot;Jeremy&quot;
1993: Best Metal/Hard Rock Video - &quot;Jeremy&quot;
1993: Best Direction - Mark Pellington for &quot;Jeremy&quot;

Grammy Awards:

1996: Best Hard Rock Performance - &quot;Spin the Black Circle&quot;

